title: Canadian Liberal Party, Justin Trudeau Get To Work
text: After a historic election on October 19 that saw the highest Canadian voter turnout since 1993, a new Trudeau has become the prime minister-designate. The Liberal Party of Canada swept the Conservatives to the curb, scoring 184 possible seats in the Canadian House of Commons and moving the Conservative Party back to Official Opposition status....
